OVERVIEW
--------

CiviQual Stats is dual-licensed:

- FREE TIER (MIT License): Yellow Belt and basic Green Belt statistical
  tools for basic SPC and data analysis
- PRO TIER (Proprietary License): Advanced Green Belt and Black Belt
  statistical tools

This allows free use and modification of core statistical tools while
protecting the advanced Pro features that require a paid license.


============================================================================
PART 1: MIT LICENSE (Free Tier)
============================================================================

Yellow Belt and basic Green Belt statistical tools for basic SPC and
data analysis. Includes: XmR control charts, histogram with normality
testing, Pareto analysis, scatter diagrams, box plots, run charts, basic
capability analysis (Cp/Cpk), descriptive statistics, Anderson-Darling
normality test, t-tests, ANOVA, correlation analysis, and 4-Up Chart output.

The following files are licensed under the MIT License:

- main.py (core application)
- statistics_engine.py
- visualizations.py
- data_handler.py
- report_generator.py
- process_diagrams.py
- create_icon.py
- build_installer.py
- All files in samples/
- All files in fonts/
- All files in installer/

