============================================================================
PART 2: PROPRIETARY LICENSE (Pro Tier)
============================================================================

Advanced Green Belt and Black Belt statistical tools. Includes: Gage R&R
(MSA), Design of Experiments (DOE), non-parametric hypothesis tests, sample
size calculators, advanced capability analysis (Pp/Ppk, Cpm), multiple
regression, CUSUM/EWMA charts, Lean calculators, root cause tools, solution
tools, planning tools, and advanced data tools.

The following files are proprietary and require a paid license for use:

- license_manager.py
- msa.py (Measurement Systems Analysis)
- doe.py (Design of Experiments)
- hypothesis_tests.py
- sample_size.py
- advanced_capability.py
- multiple_regression.py
- advanced_control_charts.py
- lean_calculators.py
- chart_editor.py
- root_cause_tools.py
- solution_tools.py
- planning_tools.py
- data_tools.py

